| Read RINEX v3 (14.02 MB)                                  |     0.7397 |
| Read RINEX v3 (6.05 MB Hatanaka-compressed)               |     1.2468 |
| Read RINEX v3 (2.34 MB Hatanaka-compressed)               |     0.5653 |

| Calculate TEC from RINEX v3 (2.34 MB Hatanaka-compressed) |     0.5908 |
